</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B91BC26FFA9633673230723FBED4245" blockId="62.[264,1323,284,790]" pageId="62" pageNumber="63">
<emphasis id="B95A6034FFA9633673230723FD4F422E" bold="true" box="[312,682,523,549]" pageId="62" pageNumber="63">Derivation of specific epithet.</emphasis>
This species is named for Simon Vodosek, a budding entomological enthusiast who died (at age 7 years) far too young.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
